            "failure_message": "Strong grief with sadness, reduced agency, and attention stuck on the loss, with an attachment/connection signature. Blocks shutdown/detachment and panic hijack. Adds regulation realism: a full ‘break’ requires disinhibition (low inhibitory_control), low trait self_control, or extremely high grief that overwhelms even moderate restraint. Triggers on spike or crossing."
